---
import { getImage } from 'astro:assets';
import portraitRaw from '../assets/images/pfp.jpg';
const portrait = await getImage({ src: portraitRaw });
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div
      class="about-portrait reveal"
      style={`background-image: url('${portrait.src}')`}
      aria-label="Portrait of the photographer"
    >
      <span class="about-caption">Self-portrait · Oregon Coast</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-copy reveal">
      <div class="section-label">On the Photographer</div>
      <h2>A patient eye for <em>quiet, lasting</em> light.</h2>
      <p class="lede">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse vitae purus arcu. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Cras nec velit a leo dignissim porttitor.</p>
      <p>Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia curae. Etiam consequat, nibh in tincidunt aliquet, sapien augue lobortis arcu, ac convallis tortor magna at justo. Maecenas non finibus elit, vitae tristique enim. Integer ac magna eros.</p>
      <p>Donec mattis lacus eget sapien gravida, ac vulputate libero sodales. Mauris a sapien at velit lobortis vestibulum. Curabitur dapibus, mauris nec congue pharetra, ipsum erat malesuada lacus.</p>
      <div class="about-signature">
        <span class="sig">— Josiah Brown</span>
        <span class="role">Founder · Photographer</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 160px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1fr;
    gap: 110px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1360px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-portrait {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    background-position: center 25%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    position: relative;
    filter: saturate(0.78) contrast(1.02);
  }

  .about-portrait::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(21, 17, 13, 0.05), rgba(21, 17, 13, 0.25));
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .about-caption {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -28px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.36em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--taupe);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.42em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .section-label::before {
    content: "";
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-copy h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 4.4vw, 68px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.012em;
    margin: 0 0 36px;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .about-copy h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
  }

  .about-copy p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.62;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    max-width: 56ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .about-copy p.lede::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 4.4em;
    float: left;
    line-height: 0.86;
    margin: 6px 14px 0 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-signature {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 22px;
  }

  .about-signature .sig {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 30px;
    color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .about-signature .role {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--taupe);
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity 1000ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.6, 0.2, 1), transform 1000ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.6, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .reveal.is-in {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .about { padding: 110px 28px; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; }
  }
</style>
